Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: mcview
Version: 0.4.3
Summary: A 3D / graph event viewer for high-energy physics event simulations
Home-page: UNKNOWN
Author: Andy Buckley
Author-email: andy@insectnation.org
License: GPL
Description: mcview uses the Python wrapper for HepMC to load and view HepMC events as
        3D final-state representations in (log-)momentum space, and to dump the graph
        structure to PDF and graphviz formats.
        
